:::Time Warp:::

::Time Warp wakes up.  He wonders what had happened to him::
Time Warp: What the pit is going on here? One minute im traveling with 
Airbomber and Infectra, the next im here.
::He tries to remember, and it finally hits him::
Time Warp: Of course! That other bot sucked out my spark! And i bet he got 
the others. But then, how am i back?
::He wonders for a moment::
Time Warp: hmm, the bot must've died. And that means Airbomber must be alive 
too! Id better find him.
::He starts searching for Airbomber::
